description:
Get into the groove with cute Japanese music and accessories in the Kawaii Pack! This pack features:

Three songs
- “Idol” by YOASOBI
- “ABC de Daijoubu!” from Love and Berry
- “Milky Star,Shooting Star” from maimai

Love and Berry Fashion Set
- Love T-shirt
- Bob cut hair Accessory
- Tambourine Maracas
- Tambourine Sound Effect
- Love and Berry Icon
name: Kawaii Pack
